                <section class="pt60 pb60">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="flexBox newsDetBox">
                            <div class="newsDetInfo">
                                <strong>In the Arab University Ranking for the year 2024, the University of Science and
                                    Technology - Aden ranked 25th in the Arab world, advancing 34 places in one year. It
                                    also achieved first place locally among private universities, and first among Yemeni
                                    universities in the participation index.
                                </strong>
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                By admin / December 22, 2024
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                It is worth noting that the Arab University Ranking is published annually by the "Arab
                                University Ranking Council ARU", which was established through joint cooperation between
                                the
                                Association of Arab Universities, the League of Arab States, the Arab League
                                Educational,
                                Cultural and Scientific Organization (ALECSO) and the Federation of Arab Scientific
                                Research
                                Councils; with the aim of improving the outcomes of higher education and scientific
                                research, through this classification.
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                The classification is based on 4 main performance indicators in evaluating universities,
                                which are: the education and learning index, the scientific research index, the
                                creativity
                                and innovation index, and the participation index.
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                It is worth noting that the number of universities included in the classification has
                                increased this year compared to last year 2023, both at the Arab and local levels.
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                The University of Science and Technology - Aden has also recently achieved first place
                                in
                                the QS World University Rankings, and with this new ranking it confirms its worthiness
                                and
                                enhances its solid position on the Yemeni and Arab levels.
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                Classification site link:
                                <br/>
                                https://auranking.com/
                                <br/>
                                #University_of_Science_and_Technology_Center_President_Aden
